1914   //   (Reduce(X) + Y) + Reduce(Z)  -> Reduce(X + Z) + Y
1915   //   (Reduce(X) - Y) - Reduce(Z)  -> Reduce(X - Z) - Y
1916   //   Reduce(Z) - (Reduce(X) + Y)  -> Reduce(Z - X) - Y
